i		gopher.black	70
iWe've adopted several Icelandic traditions and added them to our		gopher.black	70
iown family ones. We leave a shoe in the window for each of the		gopher.black	70
iYule Lads as they come to visit leading up to Christmas. They are		gopher.black	70
ithirteen trolls that visit one-a-night on the days leading up to		gopher.black	70
iChristmas Eve. Each has his own personality and will usually leave		gopher.black	70
ia little treat in your shoe if you've been good. If not, you might		gopher.black	70
ifind a rotten potato in there instead. Wit has a bit of a beef		gopher.black	70
iwith Door-Slammer, but they're making up. Last year he left Wit		gopher.black	70
ifake cat poop in his shoe.		gopher.black	70
i		gopher.black	70
