iI put the tree up and Leah and Wit do the decorating. Then I put		gopher.black	70
ithe star on top and it's all set. Presents slowly appear day by		gopher.black	70
iday leading up to the big day.		gopher.black	70
i		gopher.black	70
iSanta is a big deal here still. Wit knows that the real Santa is		gopher.black	70
inot the guy he sees at the malls. We've explained that he lives in		gopher.black	70
iFinnish Lapland above the arctic circle, which is why people refer		gopher.black	70
ito his home as the North Pole. We've seen the videos of him at		gopher.black	70
